<h2 id="create">create</h2>
<p>Now the A3+ images typically on photo paper have been printed out then first cut out the windows with a crafting knife.</p>
<p>Now apply a prit stick glue to the back of the cut out front windows and apply it to the back image</p>
<p>Trim the edges using a guillotine and stick the edges together using cello-tape.</p>